The food was not at all good. The place is big with few swans and makes it a delight for children. There is also kids play area in the interior, though not sure if general public is allowed there. There is ample car parking area.
Nice hotel.  Rooms are very good. May be slightly costly. Very near temple. Fair car parking area.  Restaurant is good.  Good quality food served.

Not a place I would recommend to my friends..It's popular because of it's location and there's no real competitors in Vaitheeswaran Koil. I paid about Rs 2400/- for a AC double suit just to find the TV under repair, AC remote not working, AC was making a big noise without cooling and absolutely a pathetic situation. There was not a single cup board or even hangers to hang the used clothes. I had to struggle hard to get a reasonably better room after repeatedly going to the booking office for three times to make him understand the real conditions of the room. I felt disgusted. It's just a place hyped so much without any stuff. Despite the cost, there's not even a complementary break fast to the customer. It's just another place where people are exploited, just by using their pilgrimage mindset. We don't concentrate on luxuries and all our thoughts will be on the temple visit and Lord Shiva. These fellows exploit the situation to their gains. I would recommend people to go around to find another hotel or stay at Mayiladuthrai..

i wont recommend this. When i enquired they gave a commitment for a family lunch for 35persons a week early & they confirm the same even on that day morning. when we went there for lunch they said there is now place & we gave the reservation to someone else. they made us wait for half an hour. cleared the crowed & gave space for us. adding to that dish qty got insufficient. vada was missing

I was forced to stay here as I was hectic tired, worst hotel hospitality, service. Never choose these hotel for an emergency also, no proper response from staff, no hospitality. Room no idea. We didn't stay.But food was good and tasty. Over all hygiene is less. And REST ROOM

This restaurant is very close to Vaitheeswaran koil on the road to Mayiladuthurai. Good parking and hygiene.All serving by women only. Meal quality is satisfactory. Veg only. There is scope in improving the quality.

This hotel has been renovated recently and is an excellent place to stay at Vaitheeswaran koil. It’s pretty close to the temple and has a decent restaurant. AC and room amenities were good. I would certainly recommend this hotel to friends and family

Good location. Great surroundings. Spacious room. Reasonable good food. Service good. Two significant drawbacks are no cupboard for storage and TV beams only few regional channels with poor reception.

Nice veg restaurant in Vaitheeswaran koil. I can recommend this hotel to all. Very delicious food items. Nice service. Wonderful ambience. We had Idly, pongal, Ghee idly and Sambar vada. According to me, Price of Sambar Vada is costly.
A good decent middle class veg restaurant. Food was not too good either not too bad. However the location and ambience was simply superb
Breakfast start time is pretty late. Rooms are good. Restaurant can improve food availability timings.

Location :
1. Near Vaitheeshwaran Koil Bus stand

Simple, calm and neat place to stay in. Has a small outdoor play area for the kids.

Nice and neat.  Stayed for 1 day in March 2018.  Polite staff. Decent facilities. Not giving 5 as the restaurant didn't have anything to eat in the evening at 4pm when we checked in.

even though rooms were clean some improvements required. mosquito screens for windows and quick hot water to be done. wasting 5 to 6 buckets of water. restaurant timings are also to be tweaked to suit tourists.

For Lunch South Indian meals is supposed to be unlimited. But you have to keep chasing the 6 ladies who are serving. They will say, yes we are bringing Rice and then disappear for 15mins. We were 4 of us, even within our group, everyone didn't get all the items. I didn't get Paysam, daughter didn't get Chappathi, Mom didn't get Curd etc. Go there only if you have no other option.

Near to Vaitheeswaran temple. Outside area was good to relax but room was not so tidy and tv remote was not working. Food taste is ok. We have ordered and waited for around 40 min for our lunch to arrive. 😞
Stopped by for lunch one afternoon. There was a rush of guests from a marriage function. Service was really slow. Meal hardly had any options. There have been better experiences earlier though.

I went to this hotel first time recently (april 23,24) simply supervvvvvvv

Hotel Sadhabhishekam is a good place to stay with family when you come South on Pilgrimage. It is neat and clean. But also expensive. The crowd was very less as most temples operate with restrictions due to Pandemic.

Overall rooms clean and neat , food was average was cold the dosa was not crispy was soft and soggy .we had to leave early in the morning and they promised us coffee at 6 am which they did not deliver. There was no one at the reception at 6am so we could check out inspite of prior information

Cockroach in toilet, water leakage, unnecessarily billing for what we did not need (mattress), power trip (electricity) all night, slow service -
limited choice restaurant, dysfunctional AC, noise making fan and staff with horrible attitude. That's what I paid the exorbitant amount of Rs. 2200/room/day for.

Goibibo gives me an invoice which does not contain tax. I paid the tax at the hotel (which is what GI asked me to do), but Hotel does not give me a tax invoice and state that I need to get it from Goibibo. No acknowledgement for the room upgrade charges.

Do not believe in the good reviews provided by Goibibo as they are filtering out the not so good ones.

Writing this right from the hotel and restaurant...I am staying here from 17th to 19th Oct..

Very pleasant to stay, rooms are well Maintained , the restaurant are very neat and tasty, room service good, more over the surrounding and atmosphere is like medikare , Karnataka, we have to give100% mark to the garden which gives a heaven atmosphere at night. Not that great wen it comes to food else the place has a good ambience..came here as part of an ongoing trip to vaitheeswar temple..meal is fine but other variety menu items needs to improve in quality and taste.

அருமையான இடம்.

தங்குமிடம் விலை சற்று அதிகம்.

சாப்பாடு பரவாயில்லை நன்றாக இருக்கிறது.

பரிமாற ஆட்கள் இருந்தாலும் சரியான கவனிப்பு இல்லை.

AC Room சாப்பாடு சாப்பிட முன்னுரிமை கொடுக்கிறார்கள்.

Non AC சாப்பாடு சிலநேரங்களில் நிறுத்தி விடுகிறார்கள்.

ஓய்வெடுக்க, கழிப்பறை, பார்கிங் வசதிகள் இலவசம் . சிறப்பாக உள்ளது.

பொழுதுபோக்கு பூங்காக்கள், குழந்தைகள் விளையாட்டு இடங்கள் உள்ளன.

ஓர் அழகான அற்புதமான தங்கும்
விடுதி. இயற்கைச் சூழலுடன் அமைந்த இனிய விடுதி. ஆரவாரமான உலகில் அமைதியான இடம்.
